public interface LogVersionBridge
    Provides information and functionality for bridging log file boundaries.

    • Method Detail

      • next

        LogVersionedStoreChannel next​(LogVersionedStoreChannel channel)
                       throws IOException
        Provides the next channel, given the current channel and version. Returning the same value as was passed in means that no bridging was needed or that the end was reached.
        Parameters:
        channel - StoreChannel to advance from.
        Returns:
        the next StoreChannel having advanced on from the given channel, or channel if no bridging needed or end was reached.
        Throws:
        IOException - on error opening next version channel.
